		"description": "<p>You are as brilliant as the sun. You can emit bright light in a radius of 15ft and dim light in an additional 15ft. You are immune to the [[/condition id=blinded]] condition.</p><p>Once per Long Rest, when you cast a fire spell, any allies within 60ft of you can use their reaction to cast a gaze on your brilliant self, giving them an advantage on a check of their choice for the following minute.</p>",
